ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (EZODZITI, N.W.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of some 137,432 hectares of land in the Great Bear Lake area (Northwest Territories) until September 30, 2007, in order to facilitate the settlement of claims made by the Dogrib First Nation.
